  "one_line_review": "\"Simple & Effective\"",
  "detailed_review": "<p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What do you like best about Synup?</strong></p><p id=\"\">Interface is easy to understand and navigate.</p><p id=\"\">‍</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What do you dislike about Synup?</strong></p><p id=\"\">There is nothing about Synup that I dislike.</p><p id=\"\">‍</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Recommendations to others considering Synup:</strong></p><p id=\"\">Synup is not complicated but does exactly what it is supposed to do.</p><p id=\"\">‍</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What problems is Synup solving and how is that benefiting you?</strong></p><p id=\"\">I had a client with directory listings under 20% accurate. After just one month as a Synup location that client was registering over 50% accurate.</p>",
